title: Prang (Formerly Art Street) Construction Paper, 10 Assorted Colors, Standard Weight, 9" x 12", 500 Sheets
description: Perfect for beginner arts and crafts. This 10 color assortment is ideal for young children. Colors include: White, Sky Blue, Blue, Pink, Scarlet, Orange, Brown, Yellow, Green, and Black. Works great for cutting, pasting, doodling, and folding. Recyclable.
